org.efaps.db.print

Class OneSelect

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.efaps.db.print.OneSelect

  • public class OneSelect
extends Object
    This class is used as a part of one complete statement to be executed against the eFaps database. It will normally return the object for one attribute. The OneSelect can consist from only one attribute or of a series of PrintQuery.ISelectPart
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    The eFaps Team

      • getNewTableIndex

        public Integer getNewTableIndex(String _tableName,
                       String _column,
                       Integer _relIndex,
                       Long _clazzId)
        Get a new table index and add the table to the map of existing table indexes. The method calls in case that this OneSelect is related to a FromSelect the method org.efaps.db.PrintQuery.FromSelect#getNewTableIndex(String, Integer), else in PrintQuery the method org.efaps.db.PrintQuery#getNewTableIndex(String, Integer).
        Parameters:
        _tableName - tablename the index is wanted for
        _column - name of the column, used for the relation
        _relIndex - relation the table is used in
        _clazzId - optional id of the classification
        Returns:
        new index for the table

      • getTableIndex

        public Integer getTableIndex(String _tableName,
                    String _column,
                    int _relIndex,
                    Long _clazzId)
        Method to get an table index from #sqlTable2Index. Get a new table index and add the table to the map of existing table indexes. The method calls in case that this OneSelect is related to a FromSelect the method org.efaps.db.PrintQuery.FromSelect#getTableIndex(String, Integer), else in PrintQuery the method org.efaps.db.PrintQuery#getTableIndex(String, Integer)
        Parameters:
        _tableName - tablename the index is wanted for
        _column - name of the column, used for the relation
        _relIndex - relation the table is used in
        _clazzId - optional id of the classification
        Returns:
        index of the table or null if not found
